<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>404 Error - Page Not Found</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background-color: #fdf6f0;
      color: #333;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      height: 100vh;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      padding: 20px;
      background: #fff;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      border-radius: 10px;
    }
    .container img {
      width: 200px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      border-radius: 10px;
    }
    .container h1 {
      font-size: 48px;
      margin: 0;
      color: #d9534f;
    }
    .container p {
      margin: 10px 0 20px;
      font-size: 18px;
      color: #555;
    }
    .container a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: white;
      background-color: #5cb85c;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-weight: bold;
      transition: background-color 0.3s;
    }
    .container a:hover {
      background-color: #4cae4c;
    }
    .button-container {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 10px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <img src="./images/404 error msg 2.jpg" alt="Furniture Icon">
    <h1>404</h1>
    <p>Oops! The page you're looking for is lost in the showroom.</p>
    <p>How about exploring our <strong>best deals</strong> or <strong>latest collections</strong> instead?</p>
    <div class="button-container">
      <a href="/home">Go to Homepage</a>
      
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>

